Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:33.00,CreditInfo,,0,0,0,,\N制作信息\N翻译：AI女孩小雪（https://github.com/SnowAIGirl）\N时间轴：基于 Crunchyroll 官方字幕\N语音识别：faster-whisper（日语→中文直译）\N\N本字幕仅供学习交流，请勿用于商业用途。如侵权请联系删除。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.45,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,你看这个佐佐木。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:40.45,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,据说抽什么烟能看出人的性格。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:42.71,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:46.38,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,香烟性格测试。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:50.59,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,年轻人酒会上常玩。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:52.22,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,我是什么性格？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:57.22,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,「直率专一不会出轨」。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:03.48,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,还写了迟钝且社交障碍。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:08.11,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,那段不用读出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:09.40,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,看气氛啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:13.32,DefaultTop,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,你到底听没听？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:15.16,DefaultTop,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,你笑什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:15.16,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,年轻人流行的话题啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:25.54,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,哦那个啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.00,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.55,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,听说过。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:32.84,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,不过那种东西……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:34.30,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,同事告诉我的。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:37.09,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,觉得挺有意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.26,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(434,475)\fs32\fscx90\bord1.5\fnArial Black\c&HF29CD9&\3c&H252525&\frz8.727\pos(306.5,113.5)}Best
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.26,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(434,475)\fscx90\fs32\bord1.5\fnArial Black\c&HF29CD9&\3c&H252525&\frz8.727\pos(574.46,71.08)}Intentions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.93,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,来查查。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:45.23,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生你是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:50.57,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,呃……有了。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:55.24,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,「看似高傲实则受虐倾向」。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.95,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,什么鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:00.91,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,别这样让我抽烟。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:01.83,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,真的假的。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:05.66,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:12.05,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,「表里不一性欲意外地强」。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:18.43,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,这种东西最后都扯到性。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:21.68,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,能看出作者的偏见。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:27.14,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,不过有一点说对了。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.60,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5\fnComic Sans MS\c&H1D1B1B&\3c&HEEECEC&\pos(63,51)}Dark
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.60,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5\fnComic Sans MS\c&H1D1B1B&\3c&HEEECEC&\pos(599.5,208.5)}Light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.65,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我道歉。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:36.78,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你跪什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:39.37,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,烟和眼镜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:46.66,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,很抱歉提了这么尴尬的话题。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.08,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,还让你说出来了。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.38,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我是说。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.84,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,好吧我确实讨厌那方面的话题。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.51,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(271,1)\fs28\bord2.5\fnArial Black\c&HC20F25&\3c&HF7CBD5&}Hates dirty talk
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:05.31,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,但我知道你是为我才提的。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:12.15,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,为我着想反而道歉了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:15.78,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,让自己出丑了佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:24.83,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,没生气，抽烟吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.04,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:29.71,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,说你是表里不一可能真对了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:35.42,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,一直这么觉得但不知道怎么形容。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.92,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,现在我懂了。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.18,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,表面装酷其实人很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.89,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你就是这种人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.69,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:00.95,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,刚才那根要抽的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:03.45,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦对谢谢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.83,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,啊抱歉。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.58,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,完全忘了。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:10.33,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,要帮你点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.71,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我做错什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.63,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,没生气看我的灿烂笑容。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.31,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,还是让我道歉吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.56,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你道什么歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.86,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs12\bord2\c&HE6E6E6&\3c&H230398&\frz-15.78\fax0.3\pos(358,60)}24-Hour
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.86,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs16\fnArial Black\bord1.5\c&H2505A1&\3c&HDBDBDB&\fax0.35\frz-17.37\4c&H3D352F&\xshad-2\yshad1\pos(456,70)}Supermarket S
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:40.49,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H282C41&\3c&HF0F3F6&}Yummy Mochi Chips
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:48.74,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,昨晚惹你生气就那么走了。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:53.12,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,谢谢欢迎下次光临！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:06:00.13,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我这种人配排山田小姐的队吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:01.88,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不配。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.51,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:10.52,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,请到这边来帮您结账。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:12.52,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.28,Default,GOTOU,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.71,DefaultItalics,GOTOU,0,0,0,,那两人发生什么好事了吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:35.37,DefaultItalics,GOTOU,0,0,0,,真想看看。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:01.57,Default,GEEZERCLIENT,0,0,0,,唉……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:05.90,Default,GEEZERCLIENT,0,0,0,,大热天让您跑一趟不好意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.28,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哪里哪里。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.16,Default,GEEZERCLIENT,0,0,0,,请喝茶。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.50,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不客气了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.62,Default,GEEZER,0,0,0,,请。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:23.63,Default,GEEZER,0,0,0,,您上次的方案帮了大忙。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:28.22,Default,GEEZER,0,0,0,,老板说元気商事果然靠得住。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:29.85,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那就好。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.39,DefaultItalics,TV,0,0,0,,大家下午好。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:35.31,DefaultItalics,TV,0,0,0,,五月初就开始热了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:39.35,Default,GEEZER,0,0,0,,已经换清凉装了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.40,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那挺好。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:45.86,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我们入夏才能换。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.49,Default,GEEZER,0,0,0,,辛苦了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.99,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs13\c&HF1F1F2&\bord1\frz7.56\fax-0.1\pos(211.5,77)\3c&H887E5B&}Nationwide Forecast
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.99,DefaultItalics,TV,0,0,0,,明天日本北部地区将……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.91,Default,GEEZER,0,0,0,,总之拜托了。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.25,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,非常感谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.62,Default,GEEZER,0,0,0,,接下来回公司继续干？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.08,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不用今天可以直接回家。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.92,Default,GEEZER,0,0,0,,那挺好。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:05.42,Default,GEEZER,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生总是太拼了。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:37.96,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,到晚上还这么热受不了。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:41.88,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,现在就这样夏天还得了。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.05,Default,RANDOMOM,0,0,0,,冰淇淋好吃吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:52.64,Default,RANDOKID,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.10,Default,RANDOMOM,0,0,0,,出了好多汗。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:55.89,Default,RANDOKID,0,0,0,,好热。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:59.10,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,回家路上买个冰淇淋吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.60,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs12\bord2\c&HC8E9FF&\3c&H5555D2&\frz-15.78\fax0.3\pos(358,60)}24-Hour
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.60,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs16\fnArial Black\bord1.5\c&H6967D9&\3c&HB9D0EF&\fax0.35\frz-17.37\4c&H666E7F&\xshad-2\yshad1\pos(456,70)}Supermarket S
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:09.07,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这个点肯定人多。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.61,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:15.12,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,山、山田小姐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:19.41,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,她今天上晚班？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.67,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,今天运气太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:23.04,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,感谢惠顾！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.84,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,半、半袖？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:29.76,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,给您积个分。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:33.30,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,换上夏装了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.89,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好清凉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.89,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,而且山田小姐真是……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.43,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,太……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.98,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,冰淇淋不用买了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.19,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,走了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:56.70,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\blur0.3\fnArial Black\c&H281B1E&\frz31.26\fax-1.1\fscx60\pos(400.5,169)}Ice Cream Bar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:10:00.70,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,昨天山田小姐在却没买东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.33,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.05,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你又偷看？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:12.09,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,大个子在门口晃谁看不见。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.84,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦抱歉碍事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.35,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,那为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:26.56,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,昨天太热想吃冰淇淋。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.61,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:32.65,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,但店里凉得让我冷静下来了。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.32,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:42.37,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,还以为看到短袖就能消暑。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.04,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,好烫！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.00,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,说中了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.54,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:57.68,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,山田小姐换制服是宣告季节更替。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:59.22,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我只有感谢——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.31,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,那就是不好看咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:02.56,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我没说！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:16.11,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,只是觉得短袖很适合她。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.41,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你满头大汗。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.45,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,今天确实热。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:24.62,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,嗯……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.92,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,穿外套不热？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:32.96,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,里面穿得少比你凉快。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.97,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:36.05,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,嗯。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:39.22,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你看。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:42.97,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田、田山小姐……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.10,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对不起。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.98,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对不起看了你肚子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.77,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我说……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.36,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,肚子露着不冷？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.95,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,肚子露着不冷？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.45,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,肚子露着不冷？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.37,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,{\fs22}……吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:04.20,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,{\fs20}……吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.62,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,{\fs18}？{\fs16}？{\fs14}？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:09.25,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord2.5\fnComic Sans MS\c&H414141&\3c&HEEECEC&\b0\pos(419,105)}Yamada's Short Sleeves
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.25,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:14.00,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord2.5\fnComic Sans MS\c&H414141&\3c&HEEECEC&\b0\pos(217.5,16)}Tayama's Belly
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.83,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,耶。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:13.63,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你不冷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:22.35,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,这老头真是……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.47,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.98,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,用这个吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.02,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,晚风还是凉的。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:38.86,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不想用也没关系。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.78,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:44.74,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐我是说给你披着。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.87,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不是让你穿！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.41,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你会不自在的。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:49.79,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:55.09,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,田山小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.55,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,闭嘴手臂控。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.56,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,手臂控……？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:08.89,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,略。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.86,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,手臂控什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:33.96,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这就是我迟钝的原因吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:47.56,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,佐佐木比起肚子更喜欢手臂呢。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.35,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,1)\an7\bord1\fnComic Sans MS\c&H2D2F30&\b0\3c&HE2E3E4&\move(218,190,218,110,25,1944)}flab
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:57.19,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,该少吃点拉面了。
